headline: AM Best Revises Outlooks to Negative for Agrinational Insurance Company
summary: OLDWICK, N.J., July 24, 2025--AM Best has revised the outlooks to negative from stable and affirmed the Financial Strength Rating of A- (Excellent) and the Long-Term Issuer Credit Rating of "a-" (Excellent) of Agrinational Insurance Company (Agrinational) (headquartered in Colchester, VT).
